# Capable Wealth: weekly content pipeline schedule
# 4:00 AM every Wednesday, scheduler local time.
# Generates the upcoming week's drafts so Jared can approve before the following week.
#
# Set the timezone of whatever runs this so it fires at 4 AM LOCAL, not 4 AM UTC.
# The command below is the Claude Code headless option; adapt to your chosen runtime
# (see README.md "Runtime"). It must run from the repo root so the skills and brand docs resolve.
#
# minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week  command
  0      4    *            *     3             cd /path/to/capable-wealth && claude -p "$(cat automation/weekly-pipeline.md)"
